cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CR 

The paper deals with deep neural networks and their performance in image classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also proposes modifications to the cross-entropy loss function, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of class hierarchies is also mentioned, which is a topic in natural language processing (cs.CL) and cryptography (cs.CR).
